    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p><em>These bright metal gauntlets appear to blur when you stare at them too long. Sometimes you see purple runes floating on the surface in Celestial- warnings against anyone who might mean the wearer harm. When the wearer is damaged, the wearer can choose to activate the runes and strike their attacker with magical force.</em></p><p></p><p>When attuned to by a creature who can speak @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-rules.JournalEntry.5l8QNlgPDPOHpGID.JournalEntryPage.VZggCkMcvhk0X5Xj#celestial]{Celestial}, the wearer can use their reaction to deal [[/damage 1d6 force]] damage to a creature within 30 ft. that damages them.</p>",
